+### Auto-update support
 
-`BonkHook` is built through a project-local toolchain and no longer expects a
-globally installed .NET SDK or Visual Studio Build Tools.
+Packaged builds can check the latest GitHub release and self-update through [updater.py](/F:/Python/MegabonkReroll/updater.py). Source runs skip auto-update logic and just run the app normally.
+
+## Requirements
+
+- Windows 10 or 11 x64
+- Python 3.12 x64 for source usage
+- Administrator privileges recommended
+- Megabonk running locally
+
+Python dependencies are listed in [requirements.txt](/F:/Python/MegabonkReroll/requirements.txt):
+
+- `pymem`
+- `keyboard`
+- `colorama`
+- `customtkinter`
